description: AMUNDI PRIME GLOBAL GOVIES UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, the performance of Solactive Global Developed Government Bond Index (Total return) whether it is rising or falling. This ETF offers exposure to the fixed-rate government bonds from the main developed countries rated Investment Grade. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus or www.solactive.com.
